859
01:16:26,625 --> 01:16:28,752
- ...two
- No.

860
01:16:28,919 --> 01:16:30,763
No.

861
01:16:33,506 --> 01:16:35,717
- Zooey?
- Ethan, so listen,

862
01:16:35,884 --> 01:16:37,068
I was thinking about tonight.

863
01:16:37,135 --> 01:16:40,847
Sweetie, I'm gonna be home on time for
