866
01:16:50,565 --> 01:16:52,334
- ...romantic dinner?
- Something like that.

867
01:16:52,400 --> 01:16:54,127
And I want to make him
real spaghetti sauce

868
01:16:54,194 --> 01:16:55,995
but I don't know what I need
besides tomatoes.

869
01:16:56,029 --> 01:16:57,580
